         <abstract id="aspace_afd081758209aa7f12a1260c4d031621">The papers consist of reports, drawings, correspondence, photographs, and printed materials documenting the professional work, particularly city renewal planning, of Maurice Emile Henri Rotival during the years 1944-1963.</abstract>
